attributes.name: AceraTheGreat
attributes.description: Don't mind the name, just an old gimmick. 🤧

description.en:
Can't there be friends among male and female? HO-JUN and YU-HA are very close, but never seen each other as a man and a woman. But, the day before HO-JUN went into the military, something happened. In an awkward silence, YU-HA suddenly makes a move and kisses HO-JUN. This turned on HO-JUN's switch... "We're not actually dating, but we treat each other as if we are... Are we a thing?"

---

- [Official Traditional Chinese Translation](https://www.toptoon.net/comic/epList/80997)
description.ko:
정말 남녀 사이에 친구는 없는 걸까, 친하게 지내면서도 서로를 이성으로는 전혀 의식하지 않았던 호준과 유하.
하지만 사건은 호준의 입대 전날 일어났다. 어색한 침묵 속 무언가를 결심한 듯한 유하의 갑작스러운 키스에 호준의 욕망의 스위치가 켜지는데…
'연인은 아니지만 사귀듯이 지낸 우리 사이, 이건 썸!?'

---

- [Official Traditional Chinese Translation](https://www.toptoon.net/comic/epList/80997)
description.zh-hk:
男女之間難道沒有純友誼嗎?恩愷與昊均是從高中認識多年青梅竹馬，從未對彼此有過非分之想，直到昊均即將入伍的前一天，恩愷突然主動吻了昊均…「雖然我們不是男女朋友，但你對我的好，難道不是喜歡嗎!?」

---

- [Official Traditional Chinese Translation](https://www.toptoon.net/comic/epList/80997)
